20 "§ 143-151.20. Donations and appropriations.
21 (a) In addition to appropriations made by the General Assembly, the Board may accept
22 for any of its purposes and functions under this Article any and all donations, both real and
23 personal, and grants of money from any governmental unit or public agency, or from any
24 institution, person, firm or corporation, and may receive, utilize, disburse and transfer the same,
25 subject to the approval of the Council of State. Any arrangements pursuant to this section shall
